1. *Čuje* se zujanje u ušima. (One can hear humming in their ears.)
2. Nisam *čula* da je otišao. (I didn't hear that he left.)
3. Svi *čuju* njen glas. (Everyone hears her voice.)
4. U daljini se *čuje* šum. (In the distance one can hear a noise.)
5. *Čujem* da je ona jako uspešna. (I hear that she is very successful.)
6. Ona *čuje* sve što kažemo. (She hears everything we say.)